7. ATTRIBUTION

   This software is a modernization of the historic Mirai botnet
   source code released in 2016. The original code is used here
   solely for educational and research purposes.
   
   Any publications, presentations, or derivative works must acknowledge:
   - The original Mirai source (2016)
   - This modernization project (2026)
   - Relevant research ethics and limitations

